Package com.kilpatrickaudio.elmGen

Class Summary
EEPromHandler This class manages the assembling and writing of program banks to the EEPROM for the hardware FV-1 DSP.
EEPromProgrammer This class implements the host-side protocol, programming and verification parts of a hardware EEPROM programmer for writing to an i2c EEPROM.
ElmProgram This class represents a program on the DSP.
MemSegment This class represents a delay memory segment in the DSP.
